</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 12, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 13; Column 1; Foreign Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
