</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The city of Ventura will formally dedicate six park benches -- a gift from a 
Baja California civic organization -- at Hobert Park on Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
 A delegation from the Tijuana-La Mesa chapter of Rotary International will 
attend the 12:30 p.m. dedication at the park at Telegraph Road and Petit 
Avenue.They will be joined by Ventura Councilman Jack Tingstrom, City Manager 
John Baker and members of the Ventura East chapter of Rotary International. 
</P>
