by the Tijuana civic group continues a close relationship the two chapters have 
formed over the years. 
</P>
<P>
 Members of Rotary's East Ventura chapter have donated farm equipment, medicine 
and medical equipment to residents of the Tijuana area, most recently after 
last year's devastating floods. 
</P>
<P>
 "It is a very touching gift," Dulsa said of the benches. "It's a way for their 
members to thank the people in Ventura who have been willing to help others." 
