<HEADLINE>
<P>
PACIFIC CHORALE NAMES NEW EXEC 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Gregory A. Silberman, 40, has been appointed executive director of the Pacific 
Chorale, replacing Bonnie L. McClain, who resigned for personal reasons to 
return to her home in Iowa.McClain had served in several capacities for the 
chorale for seven years. Silberman was most recently executive director of the 
Austin (Tex.) Choral Union. He will start at the chorale Tuesday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
