sets. Albert Alvara and James Sailhamer won 6-2, 6-1, 6-0, Sam Mankiewicz and 
Jimmy Phu, 6-0, 6-1, 6-1, and Rick Nguyen and Brian Singer, 6-0, 7-5, 6-1. John 
Howell swept in singles, 7-6, 6-0, 6-0, for Fullerton (1-4). 
