<P>
COMMUNITY COLLEGE ROUNDUP; OCC SWEEPS EL CAMINO IN VOLLEYBALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Mike Melcher had 13 kills to help Orange Coast sweep El Camino in a 
nonconference men's volleyball match Friday at Orange Coast. 
</P>
<P>
 Eric Johnson added 11 kills for the Pirates (6-0), who won 15-8, 16-14, 15-9. 
</P>
<P>
 Sean Roberts had 19 kills for El Camino (4-2). 
</P>
<P>
 In other nonconference volleyball: 
</P>
<P>
 Golden West 3, Santa Monica 1 -- Andy Kijewski had 19 kills and Greg Reitz had 
