<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA031294-0237 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 022131 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 12, 1994, Saturday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 2; Metro Desk 
