<P>
 'Three strikes' law -- A headline in Friday's Times may have implied that 
prosecutors are attempting to circumvent the state's new "three strikes" 
sentencing law. In fact, as the story stated, the district attorney's office is 
analyzing arguments that defense attorneys may raise against the law. 
